    <Callout title="Location Tip" type="tip">
      Lisbon Street has strong foot traffic from local residents and costs less than Center Street. If your strategy is community-first, Lisbon Street gives you better margins while staying visible to your core customers. Route 196 is worth considering if you plan to offer delivery service—the easier parking and highway access make logistics simpler.
    </Callout>

